    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="23128-102">使用 Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) ，可以从 XML 架构生成表示数据协定的 CLR 类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23128-102">Using Windows Communication Foundation (WCF), you can generate CLR types representing data contracts from XML schemas.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23128-103">在某些情况下执行此操作时，这些架构中有一些可能无法表示为数据协定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23128-103">In certain cases when doing so, the schemas may not all be represented as data contracts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23128-104">这时，可以使用 <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ImportOptions.ImportXmlType%2A> 类的 <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ImportOptions> 属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23128-104">In this case, you can use the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ImportOptions.ImportXmlType%2A> property of the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ImportOptions> class.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="23128-105">通过将该属性设置为 `true`，可以指定将这些类型作为实现 <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.IXmlSerializable> 接口的 XML 类型导入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23128-105">Setting the property to `true` specifies that these types are imported as XML types that implement the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.IXmlSerializable> interface.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23128-106">在该过程中，生成的类型可以存储任何内容，但序列化程序将它们作为 XML 进行读写。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23128-106">In the process, the generated types can store anything, but they are read and written as XML by the serializer.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="23128-107"><xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.XmlSerializableServices> 是一个抽象的帮助器类，它包含由生成的 <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.IXmlSerializable> 类型用于读写 XML 的代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23128-107">The <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.XmlSerializableServices> is an abstract helper class that contains code that is used by the generated <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.IXmlSerializable> types to read and write XML.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23128-108">它还包含用于为生成的类型生成架构的代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23128-108">It also contains code for generating schema for the generated types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23128-109">请注意，不会存储有关这些架构的详细信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23128-109">Note that details about the schemas are not stored.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23128-110">仅将名称存储在生成的类型中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23128-110">Only the name is stored in the generated type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23128-111">该类生成一个默认架构，它表示 XML 架构类型 `anyType`，并使用适当的架构类型名称作为协定名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23128-111">This class generates a default schema that represents the XML schema type `anyType` with the appropriate schema type name as the contract name.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
